              <div class="tool-card-tag">Best for beginner keyword research</div>
            </div>
            <div class="tool-card-price">
              <div class="price">Free</div>
              <div class="per">3 daily searches · paid from $12/mo</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-body">
            <div>
              <h5>What it delivers</h5>
              <ul class="yes-list">
                <li>Keyword ideas, SEO difficulty, and SERP previews</li>
                <li>Simple UI for beginners</li>
                <li>Backlink overview at a basic level</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h5>Trade-offs</h5>
              <ul class="no-list">
                <li>3 searches a day on free tier</li>
                <li>Volume data trails Ahrefs / Semrush accuracy</li>
