            <div class="tool-rank">06</div>
            <div class="tool-card-info">
              <div class="tool-card-name">AnswerThePublic (Free Tier)</div>
              <div class="tool-card-tag">Best for content ideation</div>
            </div>
            <div class="tool-card-price">
              <div class="price">Free</div>
              <div class="per">3 daily searches · paid from $11/mo</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-body">
            <div>
              <h5>What it delivers</h5>
              <ul class="yes-list">
                <li>Question-based keyword visualisations</li>
                <li>Prepositions and comparison-style modifiers</li>
                <li>Great for FAQ and content outline ideation</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h5>Trade-offs</h5>
