              <div class="price">Free</div>
              <div class="per">Up to 500 URLs · paid £199/yr</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-body">
            <div>
              <h5>What it delivers</h5>
              <ul class="yes-list">
                <li>Full site crawl with status codes, redirects, broken links</li>
                <li>Title and meta description audit</li>
                <li>Free up to 500 URLs — covers most SMB sites</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h5>Trade-offs</h5>
              <ul class="no-list">
                <li>Desktop app — not cloud-based</li>
                <li>URL cap stops big sites short</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-foot">
            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> SMB owners running monthly technical SEO audits.</div>
            <a href="https://www.screamingfrog.co.uk/seo-spider/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="tool-cta-btn">Download free →</a>
          </div>
